title: Peter Frampton 2016-03-16 San Francisco CA
description:
Here is a nice bootleg. Check my account for more classic bootlegs.

Please enjoy, share with friends and please seed :)


Peter Frampton
March 16, 2016
Herbst Theater
San Francisco, CA


Equipment DPA 461s-battery box-sony pcm-m10
Transfer M10-usb-audacity-cdwav editor-flac

Taping location The Balcony

Taper notes, really cool show, and was finally able to see one of my childhood heroes!

Its Peter with his acoustic guitar jammin and telling stories, (the inbetween chatter can be hard to hear but I cant boost the audio anymore).  His son comes out and plays, (he was the opener).

Was a really fun show, first time at this venue, have no idea why this did not sell out (I had the whole section to myself).  I ended up near a screamer who left mid show so its not horrible.  Oh yeah I got to meet him after the show, super nice guy who signed an old frampton album and shook my hand!

It needed a volume boost (went lower as not knowing what to expect), I cant boost it higher as it was near max limits in audacity.

As always dont sell it share it, "Its only a memory unless someone records it"
